   "type": "text",
   "x": 40,
   "y": 372,
   "width": 1811.2,
   "height": 15,
   "text": "The database backup, encoded-video purge (1.9 TB down to 825 GB), and `pct move-volume 110 mp0 hddpool-1` (886 GB across 32k files) all run with Immich stopped. The old WD subvolume stays mounted until the timeline, faces, photos, and videos verify on hddpool-1, then it's destroyed.",
   "originalText": "The database backup, encoded-video purge (1.9 TB down to 825 GB), and `pct move-volume 110 mp0 hddpool-1` (886 GB across 32k files) all run with Immich stopped. The old WD subvolume stays mounted until the timeline, faces, photos, and videos verify on hddpool-1, then it's destroyed.",
   "fontSize": 12,
   "fontFamily": 5,
   "textAlign": "left",
   "verticalAlign": "top",
   "containerId": null,
   "lineHeight": 1.25,
   "baseline": 11
  }
